#: lib/lynxplanningpoker_web/controllers/page_html/how_it_works.html.heex:139
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Rooms are ephemeral: everything is deleted when the host leaves or after two hours of inactivity. We don't sell data and we don't run ads."
msgstr "Las salas son efímeras: todo se borra cuando el anfitrión sale o tras dos horas de inactividad. No vendemos datos y no mostramos anuncios."

#: lib/lynxplanningpoker_web/controllers/page_html/how_it_works.html.heex:123
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Up to 15 participants per room, which covers the vast majority of planning sessions. If you need bigger groups, get in touch."
msgstr "Hasta 15 participantes por sala, lo que cubre la gran mayoría de las sesiones de planning. Si necesitas grupos más grandes, ponte en contacto."

#: lib/lynxplanningpoker_web/controllers/page_html/how_it_works.html.heex:131
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "What happens to my data?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa con mis datos?"

#: lib/lynxplanningpoker_web/controllers/page_html/how_it_works.html.heex:91
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Yes. The core planning poker experience — creating rooms, inviting your team, voting, revealing — is free forever. We have no paid tier today; if we add one in the future, it will only cover advanced features and the basic flow will remain free."
msgstr "Sí. La experiencia principal de planning poker — crear salas, invitar a tu equipo, votar, revelar — es gratis para siempre. Hoy no tenemos plan de pago; si añadimos uno en el futuro, solo cubrirá funcionalidades avanzadas y el flujo básico seguirá siendo gratis."

#: lib/lynxplanningpoker_web/controllers/page_html/how_it_works.html.heex:66
